## ✅ Verification Results

I executed a custom verification suite [verify-sprint2.ts](file:///c:/Users/Martins%20Onyia/Documents/Projects/silver_walks_backend/scripts/verify-sprint2.ts) to validate core logic under stress:

- **Atomic Booking**: Verified that simultaneous booking requests for the same slot result in exactly ONE success using optimistic locking (`version` field).
- **Split-Slot Logic**: Confirmed that booking a 30-minute window of a 60-minute nurse availability correctly creates a new 30-minute OPEN slot for the remainder.
- **Walk State Machine**: Validated the full lifecycle from `SCHEDULED` → `IN_PROGRESS` → `COMPLETED`.
- **Constraint Enforcement**: Confirmed that the system blocks the creation of a 4th emergency contact as per business rules.

